properties.SQL Query:
SELECT
    v.youtube_video_id,
    v.youtube_channel_id,
    c.title AS channel_name
FROM
    youtube_videos_data v
JOIN
    youtube_channels_data c
ON
    v.youtube_channel_id = c.youtube_channel_id
WHERE
    v.game_title IS NULL
and v.published_at>CURRENT_DATE-12;
